channel.title: Sample developed apps on Legato
channel.description: Hi guys, I have just started working with MangOH green and Legato. With the aim of security analysis on IoT DEVICES, I am looking for already developed applicationS on Legato that are more complicated rather than "hello word" program. Is there the source code of such applications available?
